reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect little table
reviews.reviewText: Great little side table. easy to assemble and it's a nice size and height. The fabric basket at the bottom is still a little wrinkled after a few months of use, but it's only a minor issue

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Super cute side table
reviews.reviewText: I needed a small table to go with my bedroom reading chair. This fit the bill. Easy to assemble. Can't beat the price. Space for my kindle and a cup of coffee; with an additional small shelf and basket to spare.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: When I first saw the box these tables arrived in, I thought "No way!", these are way too small, but after opening them I saw all the pieces and the ease of assembly. Took me about 10 minutes tops with each table to put together, and the instructions were clear and easy to decipher. No IKEA trauma here!These are very small and low profile tables, but for my purposes they were perfect. The one feature I really liked was the adjustable feet. You can unscrew them to give yourself up to 1 inch of additional height to the table. I'm glad I purchased them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars SMALL SIZE WORKED FOR ME
reviews.reviewText: In case anyone is interested in the dimensions for the interior of the tray (where you can put things), it is 7/8" deep and 11" in diameter. The dimensions given in the diagram are correct, but they are the exterior dimensions.It took me quite a bit longer than 10 minutes to assemble. I had some trouble attaching the last screw to secure the basket but finally got it.The table appears to be of decent quality, seems quite sturdy and although It's small, its exactly the size I wanted. Very happy with the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small but Mighty
reviews.reviewText: It arrived in a small box and I was pretty worried about the size. Putting it together was easy with one kind of bolt and washers holding it together. It is a little smaller than I thought it might be but that’s mostly on me for not looking too deep into the measurements. It fits well with the rest of my decor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Looks cute, but is flimsy.
reviews.reviewText: This looks just like the picture. However, the stand itself is very cheaply made. It was overall easy to assemble, but some of the holes don't match up like they should. The stand is also very wobbly. Luckily I had some strips to put on the bottom to stop the wobbling.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Match perfectly with hardwood floor
reviews.reviewText: This side table is in really good quality for the price I paid! And it matches perfectly with my hardwood floor. Great for side table or plant stand. Def 5 stars!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 13, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great product for the price
reviews.reviewText: Love this little side table! I bought these for Christmas for my daughter for her room. They we absolutely perfect for the space and super easy to put together.

Assembling the table was a breeze, even for someone like me who tends to be a bit klutzy. The package contained everything needed, including a few screws and an allen wrench.Functionality is at the forefront of this design. Whether used as a bedside table, end table, or a side table in the living room, its versatility shines through. The round shape provides ample space for a lamp, books, or even a decorative vase of flowers.I appreciate the attention to detail in the design. Its wood-like texture and color blend seamlessly into any corner, offering a subtle and unobtrusive presence.
Very easy to put together, will buy again
I was looking for a small coffee table and this one fits my home perfectly and beautifully! It also came at a great price!
